Paylocity,Web,Services,Push,Notifications,are,the,process,of,triggering,an,action,based,on,the,change,of,data,within,the,Web,Pay,system,The,action,triggered,is,the,sending,of,a,JSON,push,notification,to,an,external,HTTPS,URL,that,is,provided,by,our,clients,The,HTTPS,URL,can,have,no,authentication,or,basic,authentication,Paylocity,s,recommendation,is,to,use,the,basic,authentication,so,that,they,can,provide,one,more,levels,of,security,for,data,protection,Paylocity,is,a,Cloud,based,payroll,software,designed,for,the,mid,market,to,simplify,how,you,perform,everyday,payroll,and,human,resources,tasks,using,an,online,system